      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know once was, but this was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and was it-- it was some-- but I don't recall it this-- but he was-- I know something happened, but I think this was in '42, '43. '43, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
